[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":321},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20240715\u002F604545734\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20240715\u002F604545734\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20240715\u002F604545734\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20240715\u002F604545734\u002F":296,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20240715\u002F604545734\u002F":305},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2024\u002F07\u002F15\u002Fzero-width-space-zwsp-invisible-characters-that-break-code\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":277,"date":278,"description":18,"extension":279,"lang":280,"meta":281,"navigation":282,"path":283,"readingMinutes":284,"seo":285,"standalone":286,"stem":287,"tags":288,"tldr":293,"updated":278,"url":294,"__hash__":295},"content\u002F雜談\u002F神秘符號-Zero-width-space-ZWSP（看不見的空白）.md","神秘符號 Zero-width-space, ZWSP（看不見的空白）","604545734",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":264},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,31,34,44,47,63,66,75,78,85,88,94,101,104,107,112,118,123,126,132,138,142,154,160,163,168,176,179,186,195,199,210,215,218,224,227,238,243,254,260],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"你有沒有遇過一種狀況，明明你的畫面上呈現只有「ABC」或是「123」，但當你在執行程式碼或者是打 API Url 的時候，你卻無法正常運作或打出去，這其實有可能是所謂的「神秘符號」所造成的，這邊我們來談談這個神秘符號 Zero-width-space 以及該如何解決這個問題。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"zero-width-spacezwsp","Zero-width-space（ZWSP）",[16,24,25,26,30],{},"Zero-width-space 又稱不可列印空白、零寬空格，有點難理解吧？我換個說法或許會比較容易理解，簡單來講就是一個「",[27,28,29],"code",{},"看不見的空白","」。",[16,32,33],{},"那麼這會造成哪些問題呢？",[35,36,37,41],"ul",{},[38,39,40],"li",{},"API Url 無法打出去",[38,42,43],{},"程式碼無法正常運作",[16,45,46],{},"這邊讓我們來看一下底下這個例子，這是一個 API Url，裡面有五個 Zero-width-space：",[48,49,54],"pre",{"className":50,"code":51,"language":52,"meta":53,"style":53},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fexample.io​\u002Fv2​\u002Fapi​\u002Fhexschool​\u002Fproducts​\u002Fall\n","txt","",[27,55,56],{"__ignoreMap":53},[57,58,61],"span",{"class":59,"line":60},"line",1,[57,62,51],{},[16,64,65],{},"底下修正後的 Url，把 Zero-width-space 移除：",[48,67,69],{"className":50,"code":68,"language":52,"meta":53,"style":53},"https:\u002F\u002Fexample.io\u002Fv2\u002Fapi\u002Fhexschool\u002Fproducts\u002Fall\n",[27,70,71],{"__ignoreMap":53},[57,72,73],{"class":59,"line":60},[57,74,68],{},[16,76,77],{},"透過肉眼以及貼到 VSCode 上你根本看不出差異",[16,79,80],{},[81,82],"img",{"alt":83,"src":84},"ZSWP","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002Fcode.png",[16,86,87],{},"這時候你應該會覺得這兩個網址是一樣的",[16,89,90],{},[81,91],{"alt":92,"src":93},"你是一個正常 URL 吧？","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F1721033403511.png",[16,95,96,97,100],{},"但是這個差異卻會造成你的程式碼無法正常運作，這就是 Zero-width-space 的問題，而這也不是 Bug，而是一個 ",[27,98,99],{},"U+200B"," 的 Unicode 字元",[12,102,103],{"id":103},"解決方法",[16,105,106],{},"其實上方程式碼你就算複製下來貼到 VSCode 也看不出差異，所以這邊來分享幾個小技巧",[108,109,111],"h3",{"id":110},"invisible-characters","Invisible Characters",[16,113,114,115,117],{},"打開 VSCode 的設定，搜尋 ",[27,116,111],{}," 將他打勾，這樣你就可以看到看不見的空白了～",[16,119,120],{},[81,121],{"alt":111,"src":122},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-07-15%2017.11.55.png",[16,124,125],{},"底下也附上開啟前跟開啟後差異：",[16,127,128],{},[81,129],{"alt":130,"src":131},"開啟前","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-07-15%2017.13.00.png",[16,133,134],{},[81,135],{"alt":136,"src":137},"開啟後","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-07-15%2017.13.48.png",[108,139,141],{"id":140},"non-basic-ascii","Non Basic ASCII",[16,143,144,145,147,148,150,151],{},"如果 ",[27,146,111],{}," 打開後還是看不到你可以嘗試用另一招，一樣打開 VSCode 設定，搜尋 ",[27,149,141],{},"，並改成 ",[27,152,153],{},"true",[16,155,156],{},[81,157],{"alt":158,"src":159},"ASCII","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-07-15%2016.27.48.png",[16,161,162],{},"之後你就可以看到 ASCII 之外的字元了，這時候你就可以看到網址中的 Zero-width-space 了",[16,164,165],{},[81,166],{"alt":141,"src":167},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2024-07-15_16_29_22.jpg",[169,170,173],"callout",{"title":171,"type":172},"Note","note",[16,174,175],{},"ASCII 是一種字元編碼，它是一種字元集合，包含了英文大小寫字母、數字、標點符號等等，因此中文、日文、韓文等等都不在 ASCII 範圍內，所以 Zero-width-space 也不在 ASCII 範圍內。",[108,177,178],{"id":178},"直接貼到瀏覽器",[16,180,181,182,185],{},"還有一個招式就是直接貼到瀏覽器上，將有 Zero-width-space 的網址貼到瀏覽器上，你就可以看到網址中的 Zero-width-space 了，它會被轉換成 ",[27,183,184],{},"%E2%80%8B","。",[48,187,189],{"className":50,"code":188,"language":52,"meta":53,"style":53},"https:\u002F\u002Fexample.io\u002Fv2%E2%80%8B\u002Fapi%E2%80%8B\u002Fhexschool%E2%80%8B\u002Fproducts%E2%80%8B\u002Fall\n",[27,190,191],{"__ignoreMap":53},[57,192,193],{"class":59,"line":60},[57,194,188],{},[108,196,198],{"id":197},"gremlins-套件","Gremlins 套件",[16,200,201,202,209],{},"我個人會滿推薦安裝 VSCode 的 ",[203,204,208],"a",{"href":205,"rel":206},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=nhoizey.gremlins",[207],"nofollow","Gremlins"," 套件，這個套件可以幫助你找出看不見的空白，這樣你就可以快速找出問題所在。",[16,211,212],{},[81,213],{"alt":208,"src":214},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E7%AC%A6%E8%99%9F-Zero-width-space-ZWSP%EF%BC%88%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E7%99%BD%EF%BC%89_md_%E2%80%94_isRayNotArray.jpg",[12,216,217],{"id":217},"結論",[16,219,220],{},[81,221],{"alt":222,"src":223},"除錯除了一天才發現被 ZWAP 陰了的你","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F1721033222323.png",[16,225,226],{},"這招其實也可以拿來陰自己的同事，但強烈建議不要亂搞 XD",[16,228,229,230,233,234,237],{},"至於實現方式很簡單，以 Mac 來講，你需要按下 ",[27,231,232],{},"Control + Command + Space"," 叫出 Emoji 選單，接著搜尋 ",[27,235,236],{},"ZERO WIDTH SPACE","，你就可以找到這個神秘符號了",[16,239,240],{},[81,241],{"alt":236,"src":242},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fzwsp\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-07-15%2016.56.15.png",[16,244,245,246,249,250,253],{},"Windows 的話，則是按著 ",[27,247,248],{},"Alt"," 鍵，並且在數字鍵盤上輸入 ",[27,251,252],{},"8203","，就可以打出 Zero-width-space 了～",[16,255,256,257],{},"以上招式請不要拿來亂搞人唷 ",[258,259],"d",{},[261,262,263],"style",{},"html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}html.dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}",{"title":53,"searchDepth":265,"depth":265,"links":266},2,[267,268,269,276],{"id":14,"depth":265,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":265,"text":22},{"id":103,"depth":265,"text":103,"children":270},[271,273,274,275],{"id":110,"depth":272,"text":111},3,{"id":140,"depth":272,"text":141},{"id":178,"depth":272,"text":178},{"id":197,"depth":272,"text":198},{"id":217,"depth":2